trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of print system objects.
trans-unit.target: Representa uma coleção de objetos de sistema de impressão.

trans-unit.source: If you derive a class from <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObject>, you may want to derive a collection of objects of that class from <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects>.
trans-unit.target: Se você derivar uma classe de <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObject>, talvez você queira derivar uma coleção de objetos da classe de <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects>.

trans-unit.source: Classes within the <xref:System.Printing> namespace are not supported for use within a Windows service or ASP.NET application or service.
trans-unit.target: Classes dentro de <xref:System.Printing> namespace não têm suporte para uso dentro de um serviço do Windows ou serviço ou aplicativo ASP.NET.

trans-unit.source: Attempting to use these classes from within one of these application types may produce unexpected problems, such as diminished service performance and run-time exceptions.
trans-unit.target: Tentativa de usar essas classes de dentro de um desses tipos de aplicativo pode gerar problemas inesperados, como diminuído exceções de desempenho e tempo de execução de serviço.

trans-unit.source: If you want to print from a Windows Forms application, see the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing> namespace.
trans-unit.target: Se você quiser imprimir a partir de um aplicativo Windows Forms, consulte o <xref:System.Drawing.Printing> namespace.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects" />.

trans-unit.source: Releases the resources used by the <see cref="T:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects" />.
trans-unit.target: Libera os recursos usados pelo <see cref="T:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects" />.

trans-unit.source: Releases all resources used by the <see cref="T:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects" />.
trans-unit.target: Libera todos os recursos usados pelo <see cref="T:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects" />.

trans-unit.source: Call <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects.Dispose> when you are finished using the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects>.
trans-unit.target: Chamar <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects.Dispose> quando tiver terminado de usar o <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects.Dispose> method leaves the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects> in an unusable state.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects.Dispose> método deixa o <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects> em um estado inutilizável.

trans-unit.source: After calling <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects.Dispose>, you must release all references to the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects> so the garbage collector can reclaim the memory that the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects> was occupying.
trans-unit.target: Depois de chamar <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects.Dispose>, você deve liberar todas as referências para o <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects> para o coletor de lixo possa recuperar a memória que o <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects> estava ocupando.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Cleaning Up Unmanaged Resources](~/docs/standard/garbage-collection/unmanaged.md) and [Implementing a Dispose Method](~/docs/standard/garbage-collection/implementing-dispose.md).
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações, consulte [limpeza de recursos não gerenciados](~/docs/standard/garbage-collection/unmanaged.md) e [implementar um método Dispose](~/docs/standard/garbage-collection/implementing-dispose.md).

trans-unit.source: Always call <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects.Dispose> before you release your last reference to the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects>.
trans-unit.target: Sempre chamar <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects.Dispose> antes de liberar sua última referência para o <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects>.

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the resources it is using will not be freed until the garbage collector calls the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects> object's <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Caso contrário, os recursos que está usando não serão liberados até que o coletor de lixo chame o <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects> do objeto <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> método.

trans-unit.source: Releases the unmanaged resources that are used by the <see cref="T:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects" /> and optionally releases the managed resources.
trans-unit.target: Libera os recursos não gerenciados usados pelo <see cref="T:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects" /> e libera opcionalmente os recursos gerados.

trans-unit.source: This method is called by the public <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects.Dispose> method and the <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Este método é chamado pelo método público <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects.Dispose> e pelo método <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects.Dispose> invokes the protected <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects.Dispose%28System.Boolean%29> method with the unnamed Boolean parameter set to `true`.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects.Dispose> invoca o protegido <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects.Dispose%28System.Boolean%29> método com o parâmetro booliano sem nome definido como `true`.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> invokes <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects.Dispose%28System.Boolean%29> with the parameter set to `false`.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> invoca <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects.Dispose%28System.Boolean%29> com o parâmetro definido `false`.

trans-unit.source: When the Boolean parameter is `true`, this method releases all resources held by any managed objects that this <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects> references.
trans-unit.target: Quando o parâmetro booliano é `true`, esse método libera todos os recursos mantidos por qualquer objeto gerenciado que este <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemObjects> referências.

trans-unit.source: This method invokes the `Dispose()` method of each referenced object.
trans-unit.target: Este método invoca o método `Dispose()` de cada objeto referenciado.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="Dispose" /> can be called multiple times by other objects.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="Dispose" /> pode ser chamado várias vezes por outros objetos.

trans-unit.source: When overriding <see langword="Dispose(Boolean)" />, be careful not to reference objects that have been previously disposed of in an earlier call to <see langword="Dispose" />.
trans-unit.target: Ao substituir <see langword="Dispose(Boolean)" />, tome cuidado para não referenciar objetos que tenham sido descartados anteriormente em uma chamada anterior para <see langword="Dispose" />.

trans-unit.source: For more information about how to implement <see langword="Dispose(Boolean)" />, see [Implementing a Dispose Method](~/docs/standard/garbage-collection/implementing-dispose.md).
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações sobre como implementar <see langword="Dispose(Boolean)" />, consulte [implementar um método Dispose](~/docs/standard/garbage-collection/implementing-dispose.md).

trans-unit.source: For more information about <see langword="Dispose" /> and <see cref="M:System.Object.Finalize" />, see [Cleaning Up Unmanaged Resources](~/docs/standard/garbage-collection/unmanaged.md) and [Overriding the Finalize Method](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/8026cb68-fe93-43fc-96c1-c09ad7d64cd3).
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações sobre <see langword="Dispose" /> e <see cref="M:System.Object.Finalize" />, consulte [limpeza de recursos não gerenciados](~/docs/standard/garbage-collection/unmanaged.md) e [substituindo o método Finalize](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/8026cb68-fe93-43fc-96c1-c09ad7d64cd3).
